Manifest-Version: 1.0
OpenIDE-Module: org.openbeans.claude.netbeans
OpenIDE-Module-Specification-Version: 2.0
OpenIDE-Module-Localizing-Bundle: org/openbeans/claude/netbeans/Bundle.properties
OpenIDE-Module-Install: org/openbeans/claude/netbeans/ClaudeCodeInstaller.class
AutoUpdate-Show-In-Client: true
OpenIDE-Module-Display-Category: Tools
OpenIDE-Module-Short-Description: Claude Code integration for NetBeans IDE
OpenIDE-Module-Long-Description: Provides integration between Claude Code and NetBeans IDE using the Model Context Protocol (MCP). Embeds a JediTerm-based terminal that auto-launches the Claude Code CLI inside NetBeans.
OpenIDE-Module-License: ISC License
